From b28e5db9f9f94f176357fe74e643d0d9e476e007 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Subbu Jois <subbu@aurigraph.io>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 12:47:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(biocarbon): add BioCarbon VCC tokenization module
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Implements full BioCarbon Standard Third-Party tokenization workflow
on Aurigraph DLT — all 15 steps from authorization through burn/retire.

## Files added / modified

### packages/database/prisma/schema.prisma
- BiocarbonPartner — org-scoped authorization record (PENDING→AUTHORIZED→REVOKED)
- VccToken — 1:1 VCC-to-token, BioCarbon serial ID preserved in metadata
  - SFT/NFT standard (no fungible pooling per BioCarbon rules)
  - Full lifecycle: PENDING_LOCK→LOCKED→MINTED→LISTED→BURNED
  - Two-way bridge: DELISTED status for off-chain unlocking
- VccTokenTransfer — immutable on-chain transfer history
- VccTokenAuditEvent — compliance audit trail (all 13 event types)
- Back-relations added to Organization model

### apps/api/src/services/biocarbon.service.ts
- getPartner / upsertPartner / setPartnerStatus
- requestVccLock (Steps 6-7) — calls BioCarbon registry /vcc/lock
- confirmVccLocked — webhook/manual confirmation
- mintToken (Step 8) — records Aurigraph DLT tokenAddress + txHash
- listToken (Step 9)
- initiateRetirement (Steps 12-13) — beneficiary KYC capture
- burnAndRetire (Steps 14-15) — burns token + calls /vcc/retire API
- delistAndUnlock — two-way bridge (Steps 11a-11b)
- listOrgTokens / getTokenWithHistory / getTokenBySerial

### apps/api/src/routes/biocarbon.ts
- Mounted at /api/v1/biocarbon
- GET /partner, POST /partner, PATCH /partner/status
- GET /tokens, GET /tokens/:id, GET /tokens/by-serial/:serialId
- POST /tokens (lock request)
- POST /tokens/:id/confirm-lock
- POST /tokens/:id/mint
- POST /tokens/:id/list
- POST /tokens/:id/initiate-retirement
- POST /tokens/:id/burn
- POST /tokens/:id/delist

### apps/web/src/pages/dashboard/biocarbon/BiocarbonPage.tsx
- Partner status banner with authorization state
- Summary stats: locked / minted / listed / retired
- Paginated token table with inline lifecycle action buttons
- Lock VCC modal (serial ID + project metadata form)
- Initiate Retirement modal (beneficiary KYC)
- Burn confirmation modal

### packages/shared/src/schemas/biocarbon.ts
- VccLockRequestSchema, VccBeneficiarySchema, status enums
- Exported from @aurex/shared

### apps/api/src/index.ts
- Wired biocarbonRouter at /api/v1/biocarbon

BioCarbon compliance rules enforced:
- No token pooling (SFT/NFT only, no ERC-20-style fungible)
- Serial ID uniqueness constraint on vcc_tokens table
- Authorized partner guard on all lifecycle mutations
- Audit event written for every state transition
- burnAndRetire calls BioCarbon registry retirement API atomically

BREAKING: prisma migrate dev required after pull.

Refs: BioCarbon Tokenization Guidelines v1.0 §5.1-5.5
